\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->
The modules read RecHit collection and write a collection of seeds. 
After selecting a pair of hits the class 
SeedGeneratorFromHitPairsConsecutiveHits creates a seed that contains 
a TrajectoryStateOnSurface, the hits and the direction.

